Html Writr is an app that allows you to quickly and easily edit the content of static (html) webpages. To Install, simply upload the contents of the html writr folder to the root of the website that you want to edit. Then navigate to that location on a web browser. Install the program, and you should be logged in. The program recognizes all html files from where you put it, and allows you easy control over the content. To make some text editable just put <!--start editable-->editable stuff here<!--end editable-->. Its that easy. Included is a sample file to help you get started. Uses nicest for the wysiwyg editor.